rtfolio strategy I am currently advocating for. It is a strategy intended for those looking to preserve wealth, not those looking to take on excessive risk for growth. Given the intense geopolitical environment (tensions around</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2054524126/image_2054524126.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743263-monolithic-power-systems-big-growth-at-a-reasonable-price", "pub_date": "2024-12-10 16:14:39"}, {"id": "4743262", "title": "Gran Tierra Energy: Links With Trafigura And New Oil Discovery Make It A Buy", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/171322198/image_171322198.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Oil prices and Australian Dollars\" data-id=\"171322198\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1382px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/171322198/image_171322198.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/171322198/image_171322198.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/171322198/image_171322198.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/171322198/image_171322198.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/171322198/image_171322198.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/171322198/image_171322198.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/171322198/image_171322198.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/171322198/image_171322198.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"></p> <p class=\"item-credits\">cogal/E+ via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Gran Tierra Energy Inc. (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/GTE\" title=\"Gran Tierra Energy Inc.\">GTE</a></span>) reports links with Trafigura and recently reported a <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/pr/19930080-gran-tierra-energy-inc-announces-exploration-success-in-ecuador-and-strategic-joint-venture#hasComeFromMpArticle=false\">new discovery</a> in Ecuador and new <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/news/4339123-gran-tierra-makes-new-oil-discovery-in-ecuador-launches-jv-with-logan-energy\">joint venture agreement</a>. If we also take into account the acquisition of I3</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/171322198/image_171322198.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743262-gran-tierra-energy-links-with-trafigura-and-new-oil-discovery-make-it-a-buy", "pub_date": "2024-12-10 16:03:54"}, {"id": "4742937", "title": "Time And Tide Fix The Overvaluation For MEG Energy", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/155159994/image_155159994.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Oil Refinery Aerial Photo\" data-id=\"155159994\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1152px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/155159994/image_155159994.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/155159994/image_155159994.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/155159994/image_155159994.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/155159994/image_155159994.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_ima